column1: # Name: Share of unemployment with tertiary education, Male

# Definition: Share of males unemployed age 15+ in tertiary education that either leads to a first university degree or an equivalent award and programmes leading to an advanced research qualification.
# Source: International Labour Organization (ILO) Key Indicators of the Labour Market (KILM)
